name: Empowered Darkon's Debris 1
description: The former Crown Prince's new body was created at the very beginning of his lonely journey. Darkon went on to successfully fulfil his family's promise with the Arcana. The circle is closed. Dust returns to dust. Alprecha's child fades to the nothingness he was born from. (Gives 35% more damage to monsters and 25% more Gold/XP/CP/Rep when equipped.)
